<section id="hero">
  <h2 class="hide">Welcome to Bomb Coffee</h2>

  <div class="hero-container section">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <object data="/images/logo.svg"></object>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Spill the beans.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="arrow-down heartbeat index-arrow"></div>
</section>

<section id="locations" class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Find a location near you.</h2>
  <div class="border"></div>
  <div class="input-container">
    <input type="text" name="location" placeholder="Enter your city, province, postal code...">
    <a href="#" class="button">SEARCH</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="aboutus">
  <div class="section-overlay">
  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Spill it.</h2>
    <div class="border"></div>
    <p>Have you had a bad day? A bad week? Has something gone horribly wrong and you need to vent with a hot drink in your hand? Maybe you just want to catch up with the girls and share some hot goss. Whatever the occasion, whatever the issue, spill it here. Let our cozy cafe consume you and all of your distress, and enjoy our signature Bomb Coffee. Guarunteed to make you feel amazing.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="blends">
  <h2 class="section-title">Learn about our Bomb Beans.</h2>
  <div class="border"></div>
  <img src="/images/leafs.png" alt="leaf decoration" class="bckgd-item">
  <div class="tile-container">
    {{#each beans}}
      <div class="tile" data-img="{{image}}">
        <a href="/beans/{{name}}">
          <div class="section-overlay">
            <p>{{name}}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
    <img src="/images/leafs.png" alt="leaf decoration" class="bckgd-item">
</section>

<section id="calltoaction">
  <div class="section-overlay">
  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Come spill the beans with us.</h2>
    <div class="border"></div>
    <p>Grab a cup to stay or to go, and feel your misery dissolve into your Bomb Coffee.</p>
    <div class="logo-container">
      <img src="/images/logo-white.svg" alt="Bomb Coffee Logo">
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>
